The paper focuses on image generation and disentanglement of multiple factors such as background, object pose, shape, and texture. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper uses a generative model and adversarial training, which are common techniques in artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of bounding boxes, which are commonly used in graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM) applications.
